               <p>934. 
               <persName id="t17841020-1-defend44" type="defendantName">
                  PORTER 
                  RIDOUT
               <interp inst="t17841020-1-defend44" type="surname" value="RIDOUT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17841020-1-defend44" type="given" value="PORTER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17841020-1-defend44" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t17841020-1-off1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17841020-1-off1" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17841020-1-off1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="murder"></interp>
               that he, not having the fear of God before his eyes, but being moved and seduced by the instigation of the Devil, on the <rs id="t17841020-1-cd2" type="crimeDate">7th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17841020-1-off1 t17841020-1-cd2"></join>, in the 24th year of his Majesty's reign, with force and arms, at London, in the parish of St. James's, Duke's-place, upon 
                     
                        <persName id="t17841020-1-victim46" type="victimName">
                           Moses 
                           Lazarus
                        <interp inst="t17841020-1-victim46" type="surname" value="Lazarus"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17841020-1-victim46" type="given" value="Moses"></interp>
