                   WHITCOMBE
               <interp inst="t17841020-1-person71" type="surname" value="WHITCOMBE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17841020-1-person71" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17841020-1-person71" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I have known him thirty years, I never knew any harm by him, I lived in the parish with him fifteen years, he is an harmless, innoffensive man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17841020-1-person72">
                  THOMAS
                   HOWES
               <interp inst="t17841020-1-person72" type="surname" value="HOWES"></interp>
