               <p>I have known Mr. Ridout upwards of twenty years, a very humane, quiet man.</p>
               <p>- TIMSON sworn.</p>
               <p>I have known him about fifteen or sixteen years, I have ever known him, from the connections I have had with him, a very quiet, peaceable, good kind of man.</p>
