               <p>I have known him above twenty years, a very good character as ever I knew, a good natured man, and I look upon him to be an inoffensive man.</p>
               <p>- LOWDELL sworn.</p>
               <p>I always knew him to be a very honest, peaceable, quiet man; I have known him these twenty years.</p>
