                     <interp inst="t17841020-1-verdict4" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Not Guilty on the Coroner's Inquisition.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Lord LOUGHBOROUGH.</p>
